\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \sl264\slmult1\qc\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::1>\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I was deeply sorry to hear of your fathers death, he was a dear friend, great commander and an honorable man.}
