\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  So officially this letter is a summons to the capital to be inducted by the king as one of his commanders. I chose to be the one to send you this as I knew your father and wanted to take this opportunity to say Id be happy to train you.}
